## Default



### 1. Remove Holiday



***Endpoint:***

```bash
Method: DELETE
Type: RAW
URL: localhost:3000/api/hr/calendars/holidays
```


***Headers:***

| Key | Value | Description |
| --- | ------|-------------|
| Content-Type | application/json |  |



***Body:***

```js        
{
	"calendarId": "d4f8955f-e2e4-4dac-af59-7846edfdd763",
	"day": "2020-07-19"
}
```



### 2. Edit Holiday
